    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>&nbsp;Storm Oropin</p>\n<p>You channel a bolt of lighting to burst from yourself. All creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] take [[/r {4d12}[electricity]]]{4d12 electricity damage} and must make a @Check[type:reflex|basic:true|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.classOrSpellDC.value)]. The DC is the higher of your class DC and your spell DC. On a failed save the target is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 1} for 1 round. You can&rsquo;t use Lightning Blast again for [[/r 1d4 #Lightning Blast Recharge]] rounds. This damage increases by 1d12 at level 17.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[/r ceil(@actor.level/4)d12[electricity]]]{Roll for Damage}</p>"
